{"tid":33695,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［集合Li登仔力量］勇前事件懶人包","createTime":"2016-12-11T03:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T13:53:10.000Z","uid":6818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"97c801d177c035c03c42c2252f740604816ef199","tid":33695,"uid":6818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T03:48:34.000Z","msg":"各位巴打你地好，唔知你地有冇聽過勇武前線，如果有聽過應該知道騎劫呢件事，呢件事嘅嚴重性十分大，但係就冇乜人關注，希望大家集合力量，幫一幫到手。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>事發經過</strong></span><br />\n2016年8月20號，勇武前線嘅創辦人喺勇武前線個後備Page出咗篇文，話勇前內部不斷變質同被滲透，fb page上面嘅嘢都越嚟越唔對路，組織同個Page而家就畀人騎劫咗，所以後備Page就會營運，由原有班底管理。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">後備Page嘅名叫「勇武前綫- 士啤」</span><br />\n原文：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/valiantfrontier/posts/565148080356496\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fvaliantfrontier%2Fposts%2F565148080356496&d=UdQ80mGmhU99QR1A6je6rH8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=bd1ad8ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/valiantfrontier/posts/565148080356496</a><br />\n之後過咗一日（8月21日），被騎劫個page<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Page嘅名叫「勇武前綫 」</span><br />\n就出篇聲名，話勇前創辦人係向第三方透露成員名單及其他機密資料，最終一致通過不信任動議，再話創辦人不忿有關決議，造謠生事。原文：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkvaliant/posts/1148800101829917:0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkvaliant%2Fposts%2F1148800101829917%3A0&d=UdQ80mGmhU99QR1A6je6rH8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=0174cdab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkvaliant/posts/1148800101829917:0</a><br />\n喺同一日，創辦人再出聲眀反駁騎劫者，話騎劫者從來未有提出任何有成員透露組織資料證據，反而一直以此事為由，迫害異見者，加上一直以來勇前架構鬆散，又何來紀律聆訊一說，今日騎劫者的聲明，可謂無稽之談。<br />\n<br />\n至於創辦人所謂「主動退出」勇前一說，是由於當日騎劫者，直指批評勇前的網友為「嘍囉」，於Facebook侮辱同路人，其後本人私底下曾表示指完成組織「手尾」，將會離開及解散勇前，之後騎劫者先發制人，解除創辦人Fb page admin權限。<br />\n<br />\n原文：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/valiantfrontier/posts/565464586991512\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fvaliantfrontier%2Fposts%2F565464586991512&d=UdQ80mGmhU99QR1A6je6rH8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=8d152eb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/valiantfrontier/posts/565464586991512</a><br />\n創辦人之後就話勇前嘅官方網站，官方電郵同Instagram帳號，仍然由原本管理班底一齊管理，大家仍然可以透過以下方法搵到佢地<br />\n官方網站 <a href=\"http://hkvaliant.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkvaliant.org&d=UdQ80mGmhU99QR1A6je6rH8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=b29e642f\" target=\"_blank\">hkvaliant.org</a><br />\n官方電郵 [url]info@hkvaliant.org[/url]<br />\nInstagram @valiant_frontier<br />\n直到11月，創辦人就再開一個Telegram Channel。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://telegram.me/hkvaliant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.me%2Fhkvaliant&d=UdQ80mGmhU99QR1A6je6rH8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=3cc5acf0\" target=\"_blank\">https://telegram.me/hkvaliant</a><br />\n11月12號，創辦人再講更多勇前黑幕，指勇前其中一位騎劫者  <span style=\"color: red;\">張善健 </span>   於早前區議會選舉舞弊案篤灰，導致有路人被判入獄兩年半及兩年四個月。<br />\n<br />\n以特赦證人嘅張善健，就係勇前騎劫者之一。本應同為被告，之後轉做污點證人，出賣抗爭者。<br />\n<br />\n同時，張善健因有官司在身，退出勇前成員群組。騎劫者對於張善健篤魁一事，對組織成員絕口不提，成員蒙在鼓裏。詢問此事時，亦沒有得到正面回覆，包庇張善健，狼狽為奸。<br />\n<br />\n直至今年八月，特赦證人張善健完成作供，成功篤魁後，張善健重返勇武前綫，騎劫者對此事繼續絕口不提。<br />\n原文：[url]<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/valiantfrontier/posts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fvaliantfrontier%2Fposts%2F&d=UdQ80mGmhU99QR1A6je6rH8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=4289638a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/valiantfrontier/posts/</a><br />\n613317265539577:0[/url]<br />\n12月1號，勇前創辦人接受低俗頻道節目《淪陷》專訪。<br />\n<br />\n節目：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fnGzfYNN4qw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfnGzfYNN4qw&d=UdQ80mGmhU99QR1A6je6rH8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=809017f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fnGzfYNN4qw</a><br />\n<br />\n原文： <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/valiantfrontier/posts/632486246956012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fvaliantfrontier%2Fposts%2F632486246956012&d=UdQ80mGmhU99QR1A6je6rH8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=334d5d30\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/valiantfrontier/posts/632486246956012</a><br />\n過咗3日之後，勇前創辦人指自己被騎劫者要脅公開個人資料：<br />\n<br />\n自從將騎劫事件還原並公諸於世之後，本來屬於我地嘅專頁成為騎劫者龐大嘅輿論機器，用無稽之談之聲明，去抹黑我地。無奈嘅係，我地始終一直處於弱勢，後備專頁所得嘅迴響亦唔夠騎劫者大。我哋喺Facebook，喺節目公開張善健篤灰等佢地所做嘅惡行。現時換來嘅係，騎劫者欲重施故技，要脅公開我地兩個個人資料。喺我地仲有勇氣去出呢篇文時，兩位創辦人個人資料隨時滿天飛，希望大家能夠幫一個忙，將我地一直以來所面對嘅事分享開去，令大家知道而家已被騎劫嘅專頁係幾咁危險，更多人知道佢地嘅惡行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/valiantfrontier/posts/636620766542560\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fvaliantfrontier%2Fposts%2F636620766542560&d=UdQ80mGmhU99QR1A6je6rH8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=e9bf4278\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/valiantfrontier/posts/636620766542560</a><br />\n創辦人出完篇文後，直到而家個Page冇再更新。所以我而家出個post叫各位巴打幫手，創辦人而家十足十李波咁，失去免於恐懼嘅自由。而勇前班人，喺區域法院篤灰，又要脅公開個人資料，竟然冇乜人關注。請各位巴打幫一幫創辦人。"},{"pid":"f9f2ef453689246f26c0320191133d934993b801","tid":33695,"uid":6818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T03:49:43.000Z","msg":"有Facebook網民搵到要脅爆人個人資料嘅騎劫者Contact<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/f4900287075b2362d90cacdbfc71a6cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Ff4900287075b2362d90cacdbfc71a6cf.jpg&h=7d9f5b62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/c4ae925efbfd5a0290614d686dc3e8e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fc4ae925efbfd5a0290614d686dc3e8e7.jpg&h=15a4e403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/b31951a8fd918c4484dc248b9b7ee17f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fb31951a8fd918c4484dc248b9b7ee17f.jpg&h=aeeaba7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n要脅爆人個人資料條友電話號碼係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">63116411</span></span>"},{"pid":"cbc76716e29c1459bd3547a64bf779e8bccafbb1","tid":33695,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T04:05:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe239260723f4201ad70680e5598b9159d0d99f5","tid":33695,"uid":6818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T04:40:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2 long cant read ar ching</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幫手share都好，而家創辦人失蹤埋，Facebook Page PM都冇覆，變咗李波咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b66c6aab32ac732cca1f29a870987f3a4567cc4","tid":33695,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T04:53:24.000Z","msg":"唔知信邊方好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9146dff25afd0e1f0d98adbc0d7fa9310d8bda6","tid":33695,"uid":6818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:51:49.000Z","msg":"如果係私怨我諗都冇人去理，但係我見到有人將篤灰做污點證人而不被檢控嘅事實公諸於世而受到恐嚇，要脅，我真係做唔到姑息養奸"},{"pid":"225ff9a4e6c3f8e8f5e275cc7bef53204c435d84","tid":33695,"uid":6818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a33d84e80b775ba6539628f21df2c63138d1d396","tid":33695,"uid":6818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7094aa5db979d5bf02bf19594c911fba499ecde","tid":33695,"uid":6818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:13:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3f8e01f3057c1d4f62313f2f988e3ab617997a","tid":33695,"uid":6818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T13:20:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2800dd095d234fa0b16106672700b1b0b35db42e","tid":33695,"uid":6818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8392a1013658cfad6f0cda897cdd64da6bc4082f","tid":33695,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:23:57.000Z","msg":"可能我蠢, 睇完巴打嘅合集都係唔太明發生咩事&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n一個組織冇理由只係靠個page嚟做維繫同發聲嘅唯一方法架, 唔通俾人劫咗個page就會冧檔咩?"},{"pid":"d445ad57e4517c105ba26e717c7ef6c82403dad2","tid":33695,"uid":6818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:46:20.000Z","msg":"我理解嘅係成個組織被人騎劫咗，之後創辦人就將騎劫班人嘅仆街野爆出嚟，叫大家小心啲。結果而家班人就要脅佢。建議你都係上佢地個後備Page去了解。"},{"pid":"397c778ecc008f71a27aacbd6d0e79a59b68e8a2","tid":33695,"uid":6818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T14:54:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f337d9b9e47e164c3f9a6245aae4e7decda3c5","tid":33695,"uid":6818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:16:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.usedcarshongkong.com/usedcars/view/4593.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.usedcarshongkong.com%2Fusedcars%2Fview%2F4593.html&d=UdQ80mGmhU99QR1A6je6rH8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=e7723803\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.usedcarshongkong.com/usedcars/view/4593.html</a><br />\n<br />\n我Google到要脅篤灰條友賣車，原來叫Hilton Lee，有冇人識佢"},{"pid":"851fa8f014da0b0f08c2143da6caa6ac5abec753","tid":33695,"uid":6818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T15:53:08.000Z","msg":"Google到Hilton lee 嘅事蹟<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xcadps64\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxcadps64&h=a598b801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1pz43sgr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1pz43sgr&h=71580494&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9mnke4or\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9mnke4or&h=06c9b006&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢條友就係要脅爆本土派資料嘅仆街<br />\n請各位巴打幫手Share"},{"pid":"7df76070997e4523e99f38e4c4fb069efd46f73e","tid":33695,"uid":62579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T16:19:22.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"f99605cf4858e8bfb061a9fcab2eb380f27d8a53","tid":33695,"uid":65659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T16:33:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知信邊方好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我識創辦人<br />\n佢地走之前已經冇話事權<br />\n比果個乜撚R2D2同乜撚MJ搶左話事權"},{"pid":"35a1ee3496ba0ff1a8c2c09d2a2d85064a178976","tid":33695,"uid":6818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:53:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">暫時追查到嘅資料：<br />\n<br />\nHILTON LEE KA FAI<br />\n<br />\n身份：勇前騎劫者<br />\n<br />\n事蹟：<br />\n1.將創辦人踢出Facebook Admin<br />\n<br />\n2.冇證據低下公開話創辦人向第三方透露成員名單及其他機密資料。再要脅公開創辦人資料<br />\n<br />\n3.包庇另一個篤灰撚張善健<br />\n<br />\nFacebook :HILTON LEE KA FAI<br />\n<br />\n傳送門：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/homersimponson\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhomersimponson&d=UdQ80mGmhU99QR1A6je6rH8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=f3db1429\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/homersimponson</a><br />\n<br />\n電話號碼：63116411<br />\n<br />\n資料就係暫時有咁多，睇下追唔追查到張善健資料，各位巴打有任何資料放上嚟，集合連登仔力量</span></span>"}]}